  "prompt": "Good libraries in old Rajendra Nagar?",
  "response": "Old Rajendra Nagar in Delhi is known for its educational atmosphere and has several libraries that cater to students and book lovers. Some of the notable libraries in the area include:\n\n1. **Rajendra Nagar Library**: A public library that has a decent collection of books across various genres and subjects.\n\n2. **Saraswati Public Library**: This library offers a range of academic and leisure reading materials, making it suitable for students and general readers.\n\n3. **Daryaganj Book Market**: While not a library, this famous book market is close to Rajendra Nagar and has numerous second-hand book stalls where you can find affordable books.\n\n4. **Private Coaching Center Libraries**: Many coaching centers in the area also have their libraries, which often cater to students preparing for competitive exams.\n\n5. **School Libraries**: Several schools in and around Rajendra Nagar have libraries that may be accessible to the public after school hours or through membership.\n\nAlways check for the latest information regarding timings and membership rules before visiting.",
